title: Syllabus mentioned in ERP
text: Single and multiple degrees of freedom system, damped and undamped, numerical integration schemes, modal analysis for undamped and damped systems. Wind and earthquake forces, stationary, non stationary and random processes; behaviour of chimneys, bridges and high rise buildings, structural ductility.
